replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"衛生如何"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"我呢邊環境唔會太差<br />\n因為唔會似餐廳一樣要洗餐具<br />\n所以通常可以開好細水洗野<br />\n唔會整到周圍都系水<br />\n然後D人行過水就成堆黑水系地板"},{"pid":"2458edc016169278e45200e6dabd140b77cf5df9","tid":797574,"uid":197161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"茉香奶綠 點整 我覺得好好飲"},{"pid":"af3048bf13c6d5cec28e4f470b7c54b0489cac01","tid":797574,"uid":201795,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2458edc016169278e45200e6dabd140b77cf5df9","tid":797574,"uid":197161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"茉香奶綠 點整 我覺得好好飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:52:41.000Z","msg":"奶粉加綠茶 攪拌<br />\n加冰 糖 放攪拌機<br />\ndone<br />\n份量唔比講，當初簽左約<br />\n你自己上網search<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568bb2b26c264446cb85389c8e8d79aa8a249db1","tid":797574,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"你地係用奶粉唔係用奶精？"},{"pid":"90d914344977097ca5c6c2551e57ec43519e4542","tid":797574,"uid":87108,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"飲過一次鐵觀音珍珠奶茶勁難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6873d1dbe010b700a4a1e7597171b9406ffcd63b","tid":797574,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec172589ab08ceb89d6e7ccfa2ec79e639526af1","tid":797574,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T00:35:16.000Z","msg":"翡翠檸檬茶個翡翠係講啲茶定檸檬?<br />\n我女朋友話翡翠檸檬係隻品種<br />\n我上網查就話係比例"},{"pid":"5f2d28a0e5d1e05ee3b7b4ebd411c56b3a68c888","tid":797574,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec172589ab08ceb89d6e7ccfa2ec79e639526af1","tid":797574,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T00:35:16.000Z","msg":"翡翠檸檬茶個翡翠係講啲茶定檸檬?